    <abstract id="aspace_23338e8e5be3fcac64753eee258f2cd0">The Dr. Joseph Pfeifer papers, circa 1900-2013, include materials related to the life and career of Dr. Pfeifer: his work as a physician in Brooklyn; as a member of the U.S. House of Representatives representing parts of Greenpoint, Williamsburg, and Bushwick from 1935 to 1951; and papers related to his family and personal life.</abstract>
